<p class="govuk-body">This pattern allows a user to match their business with HMRC so they can continue to use a digital service.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="when-to-use">When to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Use this pattern where a user is required to provide their business details to ensure they can use a digital service.
<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="when-not-to-use">When not to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Do not use this pattern when the user needs to add different kinds of information that do not relate to each other.</p>

